data.meta_description: Discover our Philodendron (Philodendron Birkin), Le Fantastique By Charlot in large size. Plant to personalize directly online. Fast delivery anywhere in France.
data.text:
Latin name: Philodendron Birkin

Dressed in his finest regalia, Le Fantastique prides himself on turning heads. With him, there's no false humility: what he wants is to shine.

All our plants are carefully selected from the best French and European growers. Our ceramic pots are hand-made and hand-painted in Portugal.

Regular watering, always in small quantities:

1 to 2 times a week spring/summer

1 every 10-15 days autumn/winter

Be sure to let the soil dry out well between waterings

Mist the leaves with water to keep them moist.

Le Fantastique needs a bright environment. In winter, keep it away from radiators and draughts. Your Fantastique will appreciate fertiliser every fortnight in spring/summer and once a month in autumn/winter.

Keep it out of direct sunlight to avoid burning the leaves and excess water, which can cause the roots to mildew.
